{"id":"anak","term":"Anak","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Long-necked, the son of Arba, father of the Anakim (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joshua 15:13\">Josh. 15:13</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joshua 21:11\">21:11</a>, Heb. <em>Anok</em>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Joshua 15:13","Joshua 21:11"]}